    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="section-title">Designed from real veterinary experience</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">
          VetoProtec was founded to bring practical innovation to veterinary teams. Every product is developed from real clinical observations,
          then refined for safer handling, better workflow and improved day-to-day usability.
